title: Water Over Schoodic Lake Road Brownville ! (Three Rivers Community of Maine)
text: ( Source : Three Rivers Community of Maine ) PISCATAQUIS LAW ENFORCEMENT REPORTED WATER ACROSS SCHOODIC LAKE ROAD IN BROWNVILLE. THERE HAVE ALSO BEEN REPORTS OF VEHICLE ACCIDENTS DUE TO HYDROPLANING. DRIVERS ARE URGED TO USE CAUTION
